### Booking Milestones API Tests
### Base URL for the API

@baseUrl = http://localhost:4080/api/v1
@token = {{loginResponse.response.body.token}}

### ===============================
### AUTHENTICATION
### ===============================

# @name loginResponse
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/email/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@cody.inc",
  "password": "password"
}

### ===============================
### BOOKING MILESTONES CRUD
### ===============================

### Get all milestones
GET {{baseUrl}}/booking-milestones
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get milestones for a specific booking
GET {{baseUrl}}/booking-milestones?booking_id=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get milestone by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/booking-milestones/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create a milestone manually
POST {{baseUrl}}/booking-milestones
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "booking_id": 1,
  "name": "Initial Consultation",
  "description": "Complete initial consultation with customer to understand requirements",
  "sequence_order": 1,
  "payment_percent": 30.00,
  "payment_amount": 450.00,
  "auto_approve_after_hours": 48
}

### Create milestones from template
POST {{baseUrl}}/booking-milestones/from-template
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "booking_id": 1,
  "service_id": 1
}

### ===============================
### MILESTONE STATUS TRANSITIONS
### ===============================

### Start milestone (PENDING -> IN_PROGRESS)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/booking-milestones/1/start
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "provider_notes": "Starting work on this milestone"
}

### Complete/Submit milestone (IN_PROGRESS -> SUBMITTED)
### This sets submitted_at for auto-approval tracking
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/booking-milestones/1/complete
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "provider_notes": "Milestone completed. Please review and approve."
}

### Approve milestone (SUBMITTED -> APPROVED)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/booking-milestones/1/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer_notes": "Great work! Approved."
}

### Request revision (SUBMITTED -> REJECTED)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/booking-milestones/1/request-revision
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rejection_reason": "Please make these adjustments..."
}

### ===============================
### AUTO-APPROVAL TESTING
### ===============================

### Note: Auto-approval runs as a cron job every hour.
### To test, create a milestone with short auto_approve_after_hours:

### Create a milestone with 1-hour auto-approval
POST {{baseUrl}}/booking-milestones
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "booking_id": 1,
  "name": "Quick Review Milestone",
  "description": "This milestone will auto-approve after 1 hour if not manually approved",
  "sequence_order": 5,
  "payment_percent": 10.00,
  "payment_amount": 150.00,
  "auto_approve_after_hours": 1
}

### Submit the milestone to trigger submitted_at
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/booking-milestones/1/complete
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "provider_notes": "Submitted for auto-approval testing"
}

### Check milestone status - should show submitted_at and auto_approve_after_hours
GET {{baseUrl}}/booking-milestones/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===============================
### UPDATE & DELETE
### ===============================

### Update milestone
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/booking-milestones/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Milestone Name",
  "description": "Updated description"
}

### Delete milestone
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/booking-milestones/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
